                                          <xs:annotation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Orientation</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">Data is loaded from registered parent CC;  Value may be one of the following: relative positions of front, back, left or right, or the degrees arc relative to the front being zero if it doesn't align with one of the four relative positions; or the  value may be N/A if the surface is a floor or roof.</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
